-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104btr1665702651023.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/btr1665702651023.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/btr1665702651023.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"btr1665702651023\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Native Key\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This property determines whether to use the Windows key combinations (such as <span class=\"ph keypress\">Ctrl+A</span> for <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Select All</span>) to activate the native Windows functions, or to use some of these combinations to execute Uniface functions.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"btr1665702651023__p_d106013e1_d106014e1_d106015e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>NativeKey<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"btr1665702651023__table_d12512e1_d12513e1_d12514e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"btr1665702651023__table_d12512e1_d12513e1_d12514e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"btr1665702651023__table_d12512e1_d12513e1_d12514e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"btr1665702651023__table_d12512e1_d12513e1_d12514e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"btr1665702651023__table_d12512e1_d12513e1_d12514e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Use the following key combinations to activate Windows functions:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"btr1665702651023__li_d42044e1_d42045e1_d42046e1\"><strong class=\"ph b\">\n<span class=\"ph keypress\">Ctrl+A</span></strong>\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Select All</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"btr1665702651023__li_d42047e1_d42048e1_d42049e1\"><strong class=\"ph b\">\n<span class=\"ph keypress\">Ctrl+F</span></strong>\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Find</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"btr1665702651023__li_d42050e1_d42051e1_d42052e1\">\n<strong class=\"ph b\"><span class=\"ph keypress\">Ctrl+H</span></strong>\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Replace</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"btr1665702651023__li_d42053e1_d42054e1_d42055e1\">\n<strong class=\"ph b\"><span class=\"ph keypress\">Ctrl+Z</span></strong>\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Undo</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"btr1665702651023__li_d42056e1_d42057e1_d42058e1\">\n<strong class=\"ph b\"><span class=\"ph keypress\">Ctrl+Y</span></strong>\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Redo</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"btr1665702651023__table_d12512e1_d12513e1_d12514e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"btr1665702651023__table_d12512e1_d12513e1_d12514e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Use the following keys to activate Uniface structure editor functions:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"btr1665702651023__li_d42059e1_d42060e1_d42061e1\"><strong class=\"ph b\">\n<span class=\"ph keypress\">Ctrl+A</span></strong> ^Accept </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"btr1665702651023__li_d42062e1_d42063e1_d42064e1\">\n<strong class=\"ph b\"><span class=\"ph keypress\">Ctrl+H</span></strong> ^Help </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"btr1665702651023__li_d42065e1_d42066e1_d42067e1\">\n<strong class=\"ph b\"><span class=\"ph keypress\">Ctrl+Z</span></strong> ^Zoom </li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"btr1665702651023__section_gws_4b3_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d550638e216\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"btr1665702651023__p_d106019e1_d106020e1_d106021e1\">This is a static property and can be set in the\n            initialization file but not in ProcScript.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"btr1665702651023__section_q4w_pb3_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d550638e225\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qwk1688451210612.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qwk1688451210612.html\" title=\"The urtfeditbox widget is used to display and edit text as Rich Text Format (RTF), which supports formatting such as font and color attributes, text alignment, indentation, and lists. Uniface provides a logical widget called RichEditBox, which is mapped to urtfeditbox.\">urtfeditbox (RichEditBox)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612222\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612222\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Native Key Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Native Key This property determines whether to use the Windows key combinations (such as Ctrl+A for Select All ) to activate the native Windows functions, or to use some of these combinations to execute Uniface functions. \" NativeKey = True | False \" Value Description True Use the following key combinations to activate Windows functions: Ctrl+A Select All Ctrl+F Find Ctrl+H Replace Ctrl+Z Undo Ctrl+Y Redo False Use the following keys to activate Uniface structure editor functions: Ctrl+A ^Accept Ctrl+H ^Help Ctrl+Z ^Zoom Description This is a static property and can be set in the initialization file but not in ProcScript. Applies To urtfeditbox (RichEditBox) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}